Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3 (>= 3.0.0),
 libboost-system1.74.0 | libboost-system1.81.0,
 libboost-filesystem1.74.0 | libboost-filesystem1.81.0,
 libqt6core6 (>= 6.2.0) | libqt5core5a,
 libqt6gui6 (>= 6.2.0) | libqt5gui5,
 libqt6widgets6 (>= 6.2.0) | libqt5widgets5,
 libqt6network6 (>= 6.2.0) | libqt5network5,
 libgl1
Maintainer: ParthenonChain Foundation <contact@parthenonchain.org>
Description: ParthenonChain - Production-grade Layer-1 blockchain
 ParthenonChain is a Proof-of-Work blockchain with multi-asset UTXO ledger,
 Schnorr signatures, and EVM-compatible smart contracts.
 .
 Features:
  - SHA-256d PoW consensus
  - Three native tokens: TALANTON (21M), DRACHMA (41M), OBOLOS (61M)
  - Schnorr signatures (BIP-340)
  - OBL EVM-compatible smart contracts
  - DRM settlement primitives
Homepage: https://parthenonchain.org
